CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772227258
OL,3,CMurderer who left partner to die with
OL,4,Cover 100 injuries jailed for life
OL,6,FCheshire Police released Devenport's
OL,7,Farrest footage, where he claims he
OL,8,Fhadn't done anything, and denied being
OL,9,Fcovered in blood.
OL,11,FA man who violently assaulted his
OL,12,Fgirlfriend leaving her to die with
OL,13,Fmore than 100 injuries while she was
OL,14,Ftrapped in his house told police "I've
OL,15,Fnot done anything" as he was arrested.
OL,17,FStephanie Blundell, 41, was found dead
OL,18,Fby her father lying on a mattress with
OL,19,Fextensive bruising across her face and
OL,20,Fbody after being plied with vodka and
OL,21,Fice lollies by Tony Devenport, 57.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772227258
OL,3,CMurderer who left partner to die with
OL,4,Cover 100 injuries jailed for life
OL,6,FDevenport had left her to die after
OL,7,Fthe attack at the home they in Canal
OL,8,FStreet, Chester - and when police
OL,9,Farrested him told officers he had no
OL,10,Fidea why he was covered in blood.
OL,12,FBut a jury found guilty of him murder,
OL,13,Fand he was handed a life sentence,
OL,14,Fwith a minimum of 22 years.
OL,16,FPassing sentence on Devenport on
OL,17,FFriday, Mrs Justice Steyn told the
OL,18,Fdefendant he had murdered his
OL,19,F"compassionate, kind-hearted and
OL,20,Fcourageous" partner of two years.
OL,26,@{D@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772227258
OL,3,CMurderer who left partner to die with
OL,4,Cover 100 injuries jailed for life
OL,6,FThe judge said: "Stephanie Blundell
OL,7,Fdied on the morning of July 20 2025 as
OL,8,Fa result of fierce, repeated and
OL,9,Fsustained assaults inflicted by you
OL,10,Fover the preceding day or two.
OL,12,F"Her father had the most terrible
OL,13,Fexperience a parent can face of
OL,14,Fvisiting her shortly after midday on
OL,15,Fthat Sunday, only to discover that his
OL,16,Fbeloved daughter lay dead, with the
OL,17,Fmarks of the severe beatings you had
OL,18,Fmeted out abundantly clear."
OL,26,@nD@QOUtD@AOUzD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772227258
OL,3,CMurderer who left partner to die with
OL,4,Cover 100 injuries jailed for life
OL,6,FThe judge added: "She always saw the
OL,7,Fgood in people, including you, never
OL,8,Fgiving up on them. She had an enormous
OL,9,Fcapacity to love and a bright smile
OL,10,Fthat could light up a room."
OL,12,FThe court heard Devenport trapped
OL,13,FStephanie in his house and fed her
OL,14,Fvodka and ice lollies, and that he was
OL,15,F"controlling and coercive".
OL,17,FThe court was told that she did not
OL,18,Fhave a key to their house and
OL,19,FDevenport kept her bank card in his
OL,20,Fwallet, despite living together for
OL,21,Fnearly two years.
OL,26,@nD@ROUrD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772227258
OL,3,CMurderer who left partner to die with
OL,4,Cover 100 injuries jailed for life
OL,6,FMs Blundell's father told the court in
OL,7,Fan impact statement that discovering
OL,8,Fhis daughter will "stay with me for
OL,9,Fthe rest of my life."
OL,11,FHe added: "The thought that she died
OL,12,Falone in pain with nobody to comfort
OL,13,Fher haunts me every day."
OL,15,FThe court heard Ms Blundell had been
OL,16,Fsuffering with an alcohol addiction
OL,17,F"for years" when she met Devenport,
OL,18,Fbut the couple had been in a period of
OL,19,Fsobriety until they took a trip to
OL,20,FSlovakia in May 2025 when they started
OL,21,Fto drink "heavily".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772227258
OL,3,CMurderer who left partner to die with
OL,4,Cover 100 injuries jailed for life
OL,6,FThe judge said: "When intoxicated, you
OL,7,Fwere abusive, aggressive and violent
OL,8,Ftowards her on occasions prior to her
OL,9,Fdeath".
OL,11,FDevenport was arrested on suspicion of
OL,12,Fassaulting Ms Blundell 10 days before
OL,13,Fshe died but breached his bail
OL,14,Fconditions "within minutes" by calling
OL,15,Fher phone and she "never left" his
OL,16,Fhouse again after he called a taxi to
OL,17,Fpick her up.
OL,26,@vD@LOUvD@[O]wD@SOUwD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772227258
OL,3,CMurderer who left partner to die with
OL,4,Cover 100 injuries jailed for life
OL,6,FBetween July 10 and 20, Ms Blundell
OL,7,Fhad "no means of contacting anyone"
OL,8,Fand was bed-bound, while Devenport
OL,9,Fbought more than 12 litres of vodka
OL,10,Fand 72 cans of beer.
OL,12,FThe judge said that evidence showed
OL,13,FDevenport strangled Ms Blundell twice
OL,14,Fin the day or two before her death and
OL,15,Fbeat her causing significant injuries
OL,16,Fto her brain.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772227258
OL,3,CMurderer who left partner to die with
OL,4,Cover 100 injuries jailed for life
OL,6,FMrs Justice Steyn said Ms Blundell,
OL,7,Fwho had acute pancreatitis and
OL,8,Falcoholic ketoacidosis, was "bound to
OL,9,Fbe pleading with you for help" in the
OL,10,Fdays before her death, but he only
OL,11,Fgave her alcohol and ice lollies.
OL,13,FShe told the defendant: "As a result
OL,14,Fof your actions, Stephanie would have
OL,15,Fbeen in pain and fear and you kept her
OL,16,Fthere, offering little but vodka."
OL,18,FA post-mortem examination found she
OL,19,Fdied from her injuries, exacerbated by
OL,20,Fthe effects of chronic alcoholism.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772227258
OL,3,CMurderer who left partner to die with
OL,4,Cover 100 injuries jailed for life
OL,6,FIn a statement released after the
OL,7,Fsentencing, Ms Blundell's family said:
OL,8,F"Steph was, without question, one of
OL,9,Fthe most radiant souls you could ever
OL,10,Fhope to meet.
OL,12,F"She was kind-hearted, quick-witted
OL,13,Fand effortlessly stylish. Her warmth
OL,14,Fand compassion have been evident
OL,15,Fthroughout this trial and that brings
OL,16,Fus some comfort that her true loving
OL,17,Fnature has been seen by so many."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772227258
OL,3,CMurderer who left partner to die with
OL,4,Cover 100 injuries jailed for life
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Andrea Price, from
OL,7,FCheshire Constabulary's Major
OL,8,FInvestigation Team, said: "Stephanie
OL,9,Fwas loved and cherished amongst family
OL,10,Fand friends, and although today marks
OL,11,Fthe day her killer is brought to
OL,12,Fjustice, I want Stephanie to be the
OL,13,Fone who we remember.
OL,15,F"While no sentence can ever bring
OL,16,FStephanie back, I hope today's result
OL,17,Fprovides her loved ones with some
OL,18,Fcomfort in knowing that Devenport has
OL,19,Fnow been held accountable for what he
OL,20,Fhas done."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
